data.description: Beautiful 2020 built, Emerald Series 4-bedroom 3 bath concrete block home that abuts a wildlife conservation area. This 3-car garage Ormond beach home has plenty of room for your toys or hobbies. Upon entering the foyer, you'll be greeted by flowing, wood plank style tile for easy maintenance and a lasting look in the living space. Open floor plan for great family and friend gatherings with a huge quartz island for fantastic food prep, as well as command of the kitchen to keep conversation going while grabbing needed items from the 42in cabinets. 10 ft ceilings with a tray ceiling in the living room and master bedroom. Upgraded fans throughout for maximum air flow. Security system/ smart home features convey with sale. All information intended accurate but cannot be guaranteed.
